Package armyc2.c5isr.JavaTacticalRenderer

Class TGLight

java.lang.Object
armyc2.c5isr.JavaTacticalRenderer.TGLight
public class TGLight extends Object
A class to encapsulate the tactical graphic object. Many of the properties correspond to a client MilStdSymbol object.
